3   import com.mamezou.rms.external.webapi.dto.UserAccountResourceDto;
4   import com.mamezou.rms.platform.jwt.JsonWebTokenGenerator.UserClaims;
5   import com.mamezou.rms.platform.jwt.JsonWebTokenGenerator.UserClaimsFactory;
6   
7   public class UserDtoClaimsFactory implements UserClaimsFactory {
8   
9       @Override
10      public boolean canNewInstanceFrom(Object obj) {
11          return obj instanceof UserAccountResourceDto;
12      }
13  
14      @Override
15      public UserClaims newInstanceFrom(Object obj) {
16          return new UserClaimsAdaptor((UserAccountResourceDto)obj);
17      }
18  }
